The paper discusses training neural network models and specifically addresses the issue of catastrophic forgetting during retraining on new data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on deep neural network models, it is more likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) than the others.
